{"tid":1732342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各手足放下成見，救命要緊","createTime":"2019-11-18T01:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T01:36:03.000Z","uid":313635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"79f00d3dba9532bbdc9f55c17d83d99623bd967a","tid":1732342,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:11:26.000Z","msg":"我明大家一直以來由上次雨革失敗，到現時為止對大台係好反感，但依家個情況係有手足仍然肯出來但太過散亦無共同目標<br />\n其實人係足夠，只要有人組織一次肯定有過千人願意衝<br />\n係咪應該有一個一次性針對poly救手足嘅大台產生出來呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲有一位朋友係入面尋晚開始已經失聯 生死未卜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪可以放低成見 就一日咁多，大家救人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2690926cde85bdda7f7156256d7acb5f61670c67","tid":1732342,"uid":306738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:12:14.000Z","msg":"又送多一千？"},{"pid":"7e2a236e3252029af721131fa5e8934ae4ed2918","tid":1732342,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:12:38.000Z","msg":"有事鍾無艷 無事夏迎春"},{"pid":"2df6967bcd2d9dffe501aaf190a6d0ec86c685d6","tid":1732342,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:16:55.000Z","msg":"要割要屌都救左手足先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同路人少一個就一個架"},{"pid":"1647285dbc165edf0fcd013c0c74ab880a9bff4d","tid":1732342,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:22:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b32e0ad640ba114aa57340e3d8300b1bb4dd138","tid":1732342,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:36:03.000Z","msg":"全世界都出去 做少少嘢啦"}]}